    sum has automatic storage duration and no initializer, so its value is      
    indeterminate.                                                              
                                                                                
    Then the loop executes:                                                     
                                                                                
                                                                                
     for (int i = 0; i < n; i++) {                                              
         sum += atof(argv[i]);                                                  
